quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,29,"Eeheymon yo yim…ďe am, mi la…ďndaaki on jawdi e …óuum. Njo…ďdi am wonaani si wonah ka Alla. min mi wonaani ra…óotoo…óo …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe, kam…ďe ko …ďe hawroyoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe. Ko woni tun, min mi yi'ii on yim…ďe majju…ďe."
  11,30,"Eehey mon yim…ďe am, ko hommbo walloytammi ka Alla si mi ra…óike …ďe? E on mbaajitotaako?"
  11,31,"Mi wi'antah on mi…óo mari ngaluujii Alla, mi annah kadi ko wirnii, mi wi'ataa won¬īde ko mi maleyko, mi wi'antaa …ďeen …ďe gite mon …óen yawi, Alla okkoytaa-…ďe mo∆ī∆īere; ko Alla …ďuri anndude ko woni e woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe. miin ontuma [si mi wa…óii …óum], haray ko mi jeyaa…óo e too√Ī…ďe …ďeen."
  11,32,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko an yo Nuuhu, gooŇč…óii a wenjidii e amen, a …óu…ó…óinii yeddondiral ngal e amen. Addan men …óuum ko pod-…óaa amen, si a laatike jeyaa…óo e goongu…ďe …ďe"."
  11,33,"o maaki: "nganndee ko Alla addanta on …óe -si o muuyii- on ngonaani roŇčkinoo…ďe."
  11,34,"Laa…ďal-reedu am nafatah on, si mi faandike laa…ďangol on, si tawii Alla no faandii bewnugol on (majjina). Ko KaŇčko woni Joomi mon, ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon."
  11,35,"Si ko woni, …ďe mbay : o fekindi-nde. Maaku: "Si mi fekindi nde, haray bonnere am nden no fawii kam. min no ko mi da…óndii…óo ko mbonnoton kon"."
  11,36,"Wahayinaa e Nuuhu won¬īde : "GooŇč…óintah e yim…ďe maa …ďen si wanaa …ďen gooŇč…óinnoo…ďe. Wota a suno e ko …ďe ngollaynoo"."
  11,37,"Mo∆ī∆īin laana kan e ndeenka amen e yamiroore amen. Wota a yewtidoy e am fii …ďen too√Ī…ďe, kam…ďe ko …ďe yoolotoo…ďe."